title: Mobile App Developer ( Flutter )
jobDescription:
We are looking out for a Flutter Developer who will be running and designing product application features across various cross platform devices.

Key responsibilities:
  • Reviewing application requirements and interface designs.
  • Identifying mobile-based user interactions.
  • Developing and implementing highly responsive user interface components using Flutter concepts.
  • Writing application interface codes using Dart following Flutter workflows.
  • Building reusable components and mobile UI libraries for future use.
  • Troubleshooting interface software and debugging application codes.
  • Monitoring and improving mobile app performance.
  • Documenting application changes and developing updates.
  • Translating designs and wireframes into high-quality code.
  • Optimizing components for maximum performance across a wide range of mobile devices.
  • Ability to execute Flutter directly in the Dart environment.
Requirements (Qualifications / Experience / Competencies)
  • Bachelors degree in computer science, information technology, or a related field.
  • Experience with Dart and Flutter.
  • In-depth knowledge of JavaScript, CSS, HTML, and mobile app front-end languages.
  • Experience with REST APIs.
  • Git knowledge is a plus.
  • Strong team player with good time-management skills.
  • Excellent interpersonal and communication skills.
  • Previous experience working as a Flutter developer.
  • Knowledge of Flutter tools and libraries.
  • Experience with mobile user interface design.
  • Proficiency in mobile-based debugging and performance testing.
  • Excellent troubleshooting skills.
